data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Key Location & Custom Quality Abound! This quaint community is conveniently located right off SR-54 just minutes from the Suncoast Pkwy & Dale Mabry Hwy. Semi-custom pool home on a peaceful, premium, deep conservation lot sets this home apart from the rest.  Nestled in the rear of the community, privacy abounds with no through traffic on a .23 acre lot. This highly sought-after (only 305 homes) gated community has 24-hour interactive security at the gate. Once inside the gate, the outside world melts away with lush, mature landscapes. This meticulously maintained home is zoned for top-rated schools too! This Kingshyre II model has been altered from the original plan, making it larger with an additional bathroom, more storage, & more sq ft. The upstairs bonus room is an easy 5th bedroom, if desired, with a 1/2 bath & a closet. The upstairs also has a home theater & a lovely balcony overlooking the backyard. The media room includes projection/sound equipment & stadium seating (all convey with the home). Upon entry, you'll be greeted with 10 & 12-foot double-tray ceilings, custom crown molding mostly throughout, art niches, radial walls, & 5 1/4 baseboards. Designer paint & an expansive run of large 20 x 20 neutral tile dresses the first floor. The owner's suite & 2 other bedrooms, bonus room, and the dedicated dual-door office/den (not a bedroom) have wood flooring. The 4th bedroom on the first floor is outfitted as a home gym (hard mat flooring) & can convey with the home. The owner's suite provides generous space for even the most oversized king furnishings. The cook's kitchen boasts all granite, hardwood cabinetry with soft close & pull-out drawers, a large island, a GE Profile double wall oven with convection, a natural gas cooktop, a large closet pantry, down and up lighting, and built-in seating with shiplap features in the kitchen nook, too! The kitchen is open to the family room, where both spaces enjoy lavish conservation views through triple 8ft tall & 4 ft wide stacking/curtain sliders. Once outside, your STAYCATION begins! The super tranquil backyard is a haven for relaxing & entertaining! It has a covered lanai, an outdoor kitchen with counter seating, a hot tub, & a custom-designed 15x30 saltwater pool (built in 2016) with a high-end pebble tech finish, pavers, & specialty tiles. The pool is self-cleaning, with customizations like fountains, lighting, and contemporary wading ledges. The x-large screened cage opens to the almost new (built 2021) 32x16 deck!! Enjoy the great outdoors (like an outside living room). Birds, bunnies, & deer are seen regularly. The owners spared no expense in outfitting this home with many unique "stand out" extras: The Control4 Centralized Smart Home System (cable, TV, music, security & more). An upgraded premium whole-house wiring package. The whole house system also includes speakers in almost every room (including the lanai). Of course, there is surround sound in the theater. Each room has its independent sound controls operated by wall switches. An app operates the system by cell phone. During construction, $5k of insulation foam was sprayed into EVERY block for amazing energy efficiency when coupled with the Low-E windows & 3 t-stat, zone-controlled, a/c system. The garage is set up for a workshop with upgraded electrical outlets. The community center includes fitness, clubhouse, pool, park, playground, & a walking trail to a fishing lake. See the 3D Virtual & video tours.
